cdata.name: Midnight
cdata.desc: Midnight is a Proof of Work/Proof of Stakecryptocurrency that uses the Blue Midnight Wish hashing algorithm. MDThalves every year to a floor of 0.125 MDT for PoW and 0.25 MDT for PoS. Every 720 blocks is a 100 MDT coin reward, which acts as an incentive to mine on a continuous basis.
